ReviewText:
The game is good, the story is just top, but let's run through the minuses:
1. lack of vehicles (on the maps it is present, but for some reason you can not use it);
2. You can not crawl and look out from behind the corner (crouching is present);
3. You can't build a base and collect resources;
4. You can't tame pets except chickens;
5. Interaction with non-player characters to get quests is not provided;
6. Primitive parkour system;
7. Open world? There is no such thing here;
8. The intelligence of bots that play with you in competitive matches leaves much to be desired;
9. Poor arsenal of melee weapons;
10. No PvE and zombie mode;
11. No character pumping (maybe I'm wrong and just haven't found which button opens the menu of improvements, as there are enemies who have open the ability to see through walls and pumped marksmanship at 1000%).
